=== Description ===
Small set of service menu entries for KDE to help access ISO images. Mount and
unmount ISO images from Dolphin, Konqueror and other KDE file views.

=== Installation ===
Build/install using cmake with KDE4Defaults.cmake file. You might want to
check that fuseiso_mount.desktop contains the right path to where media.desktop
is installed.

Runtime requirements:
kdebase-runtime
fuseiso
dolphin or konqueror

